{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t17-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"代数式","title":"针对训练2：绝对值求代数式","difficulty":3,"tags":["代数式","绝对值","求值"],"content":"若 $|a + 1| = 5$，$|b - 2| = 3$，且 $|a - b| = a - b$，则 $a + b$ 的值是 ______。","steps":[{"title":"解绝对值","content":"$|a + 1| = 5 \\Rightarrow a = 4$ 或 $a = -6$\n$|b - 2| = 3 \\Rightarrow b = 5$ 或 $b = -1$","formula":""},{"title":"分析条件 $|a - b| = a - b$","content":"$|a - b| = a - b$ 说明 $a - b \\geq 0$，即 $a \\geq b$\n\n可能的组合：\n• $a = 4, b = -1$：$4 \\geq -1$ ✓，$a + b = 3$\n• $a = -6, b = -1$：$-6 \\geq -1$ ✗\n• $a = 4, b = 5$：$4 \\geq 5$ ✗\n• $a = -6, b = 5$：$-6 \\geq 5$ ✗","formula":"\\text{答案：}3"}]},"id":"t17-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}